<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/Screenshot%202025-09-07%20044718.png">

    <title>مستويات تمارين الجيم</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cairo:wght@400;700&display=swap');

        body {
            font-family: 'Cairo', Arial, sans-serif;
            direction: rtl;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
            color: #fff;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .levels {
            display: flex;
            gap: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .level-btn {
            padding: 18px 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 2px solid #fff;
            background: transparent;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;
            user-select: none;
            min-width: 140px;
        }

        .level-btn:hover,
        .level-btn:focus {
            background-color: #fff;
            color: #764ba2;
            outline: none;
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: auto;
            padding: 25px 20px;
            background-color: #2c2f4a;
            width: 100%;
            color: #ddd;
            text-align: center;
            user-select: none;
            box-shadow: 0 -4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        footer p {
            margin: 8px 0;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .linkedin-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background-color: #0a66c2;
            color: white;
            font-weight: 700;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(10, 102, 194, 0.6);
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            user-select: none;
        }

        .linkedin-btn:hover,
        .linkedin-btn:focus {
            background-color: #004182;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0, 65, 130, 0.8);
            outline: none;
        }

        /* زر العودة للصفحة الرئيسية */
        .home-button {
            position: fixed;
            top: 20px;
            left: 20px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
            border: none;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 700;
            padding: 10px 18px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
            font-size: 1rem;
            user-select: none;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .home-button:hover,
        .home-button:focus {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
            outline: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <button class="home-button" onclick="window.location.href='/'">العودة للصفحة الرئيسية</button>

    <h1>اختر مستوى التمرين</h1>
    <div class="levels">
        <button class="level-btn" type="button" onclick="window.location.href='/exercises-one'">مبتدئ</button>
        <button class="level-btn" type="button" onclick="window.location.href='/exercises-two'">متوسط</button>
        <button class="level-btn" type="button" onclick="window.location.href='/exercises-three'">متقدم</button>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>تم تصميم الموقع بواسطة عرفه محمد</p>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/arafa-mohamed-8015a3374" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="linkedin-btn">
            تابعني على لينكدإن
        </a>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>